All Superinterfaces:

public interface MeetupsEntryModel
extends com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<MeetupsEntry>, com.liferay.portal.model.GroupedModel

The base model interface for the MeetupsEntry service. Represents a row in the "SN_SMILE_MeetupsEntry" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

This interface and its corresponding implementation MeetupsEntryModelImpl exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in MeetupsEntryImpl.

Author:
Brian Wing Shun Chan
See Also:
MeetupsEntry, MeetupsEntryImpl, MeetupsEntryModelImpl
